com.facebook.buck.cli

Class StringSetOptionHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.kohsuke.args4j.spi.OptionHandler<Supplier<ImmutableSet<String>>>
      • com.facebook.buck.cli.StringSetOptionHandler

  • public class StringSetOptionHandler
extends org.kohsuke.args4j.spi.OptionHandler<Supplier<ImmutableSet<String>>>
    OptionHandler that collects multiple arguments passed to an option in a Set. In a list of command-line arguments:
    • The option may be specified multiple times.
    • When the option is specified, it must have at least one value (multiple values must be delimited by spaces).
    • The same value may be specified multiple times for the option. However, even though a value may be specified more than once, only one instance of it will be present in the resulting Set.
